Author: mementomorii0
Text: Exactly. I actually just ate some lettuce and tomatoes rn because I plan on fasting tomorrow. I know there's barely any calories and it's healthy, yet I still feel compelled to not eat it. Even eating nutritous food is hard for me. Consuming food just brings more guilt/shame and reminds me how much of a failure I am.

Author: scaredyk4t
Text: I feel this :-(. Especially in the last few weeks. I’ve been up like +1.5 lbs and I’m pretty underweight but I just feel so gross even when I eat a damn salad. I miss eating a normal meal and feeling okay about it.
